'''Angela Harry''' (born [[1960s#1963|1963]]) is a model, actress, and voice actor who played [[Jan Ors]] in ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II]]''. In all subsequent appearances, Ors was modeled to look like Harry.

